RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT branch_code , branch_name FROM (SELECT m.branch_code branch_code, m.branch_name , n.branch_allowed branch_allowed, t.branch_allowed branch_allowed_tmp, n.user_branch, n.branch_code branch_code_tmp FROM sttms_core_branch m, (SELECT b.branch_code, a.* FROM smtbs_restr_usad a, smtb_res_brn b, SMTB_USER c WHERE a.restr_type = 'USERADMIN' AND a.user_branch = b.user_branch AND c.home_branch = a.user_branch AND user_id = global.user_id AND a.restr_type = b.restr_type) n, (SELECT q.user_id, a.branch_allowed branch_allowed FROM smtbs_restr_usad a, SMTB_USER q WHERE user_id = global.user_id AND q.home_branch = a.user_branch(+) AND a.restr_type(+) = 'USERADMIN') t WHERE m.record_stat = 'O' AND m.once_auth = 'Y' AND t.user_id = global.user_id AND m.branch_code = n.branch_code(+)) ss WHERE ((branch_allowed = 'A' AND branch_code_tmp IS NOT NULL) OR (nvl(branch_allowed, 'D') = branch_allowed_tmp AND branch_code_tmp IS NULL) or branch_allowed_tmp is null )

(SELECT A.USER_ID, A.USER_NAME FROM SMTB_USER A WHERE A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' minus SELECT A.USER_ID, A.USER_NAME FROM SMTB_USER A WHERE A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' and a.user_id= ?)UNION SELECT ? USER_ID, ? USER_NAME FROM DUAL

SELECT ROLFNID, DESCRIPTION FROM (SELECT ROLE_ID ROLFNID, ROLE_DESCRIPTION DESCRIPTION, 'R' ROLFN FROM SMTB_ROLE_MASTER UNION SELECT MEN.FUNCTION_ID ROLFNID, FND.DESCRIPTION DESCRIPTION, 'F' ROLFN FROM SMTB_MENU MEN INNER JOIN SMTB_FUNCTION_DESCRIPTION FND ON (MEN.FUNCTION_ID = FND.FUNCTION_ID AND FND.LANG_CODE = GLOBAL.LANG) WHERE MEN.TYPE_STRING = 'D' AND MEN.FUNCTION_ID NOT IN ('SMDHOTKY', 'SMDMBEAN')) WHERE ROLFN = ?
